*** The Minimal-Editor ***

it's my personal use project.
build it only need ncurses installed.
use 'me' for start it.


** Contributing **

Please use clang-format format it. and open a pull request.

** How to use it **

Key Bindings:
Ctrl S - Save the current file.
Ctrl O - Open a file.
Ctrl N - Create a new file.
Ctrl Q - Quit the editor.
Ctrl F - Find text in the current file.
Ctrl R - Replace text in the current file.
Ctrl Z - Undo the last action.
Ctrl Y - Redo the last undone action.
Ctrl E - Toggle filetree.
Ctrl P - Enter command mode.